Azor aphútǎ̤ dǐtû́ Zadok, Zadok aphútǎ̤ dǐtû́ Akim, Akim aphútǎ̤ dǐtû́ Eliud,
Bí Khwí Herodè thè́gněhò́ ná prè̤thíphè́phú tahe lahǒkyǎ hò́ lǔ akhè̌nuô, a thè́plòdu lakálakǒ cò́. Phú a pṳ̌thè́gně tǎ̤te̤ ní̤htuô̌hò́ dố prè̤thíphè́phú yětahe alo̤ ná sè oluô̌htya pé̤ èthǐ bíkhè̌tě nuô, a nò̌me̤thyě lò̌ prè̤khǔ pacè̤̌phú nyě̤na tǎ̤palya̤ tahe dố a o dố vǐ̤ Bethelehem akǔnuô ná dò̌o tavǐtava̤ bínuô lò̌꤮ plǐ.
